```
byebug) availability_data
[{"itemBarcode"=>"", "itemAvailabilityStatus"=>nil, "errorMessage"=>"Bib Id doesn't exist in SCSB database.", "collectionGroupDesignation"=>nil}]
(byebug) system_id
"99124962843506421"
(byebug)  scsb_owning_institution(scsb_location)
"PUL"
```
In Process is correct for this item given that SCSB is returning that the item does not exist.

The host records are not yet linked to the barcodes, so the only way to look up this item in SCSB would be to look up the barcode. 32101051672317

It is in ReCAP. Most likely, these issues will be cleaned up by Monday. I am still processing the submitCollection that will link the host records to the barcodes.
